three more weeks to graduate from high school with a perfect 
attendance record in 12 years of school 
hes trying to best the records of his older brother and sister 
both of whom missed one day each in their school careers 
my brother missed a day in kindergarten for some reason 
said the 18yearold holand my sister is still mad at my mom for 
making her go to the hospital and miss one day ill beat them 
both 
holands classmates are a bit baffled by his perfect record 
youd think he was sick just one day said classmate dennis 
flaten 
