inexplicably judge young determined that all the previous 
decisions and statutory guidelines were irrelevant for determining 
when the unborn enjoy a protectable legal status the appeal says 
the appeal also contends young should not have strayed into the 
field of morals and ethics in reaching his decision 
judge young has independently quantified the value 
attributable to the existence of a four to eightcell embryo being 
