<TEXT>
tom toles the buffalo news cartoonist once 
labeled the rodney dangerfield of editorial cartooning has 
gotten journalisms most respected prize the pulitzer 
and the best thing about winning the pulitzer for editorial 
cartooning toles told colleagues who crowded into his cubicle 
