toles were just absolutely so totally gratified for you and 
your talent 
toles known for his environmentalism and outrage at military 
spending at the expense of social programs was honored for a 
selection of 10 cartoons representing his best work of 1989 
he said he thinks of his cartoons as an ongoing series rather 
