number of multiplewarhead mobile missiles on each side he 
referred to bakers comment last week that there are some things 
we just dont comment on and particularly if theres some chance 
that they are under consideration as part of our negotiations 
the issue is particularly sensitive because of uncertainty about 
how the soviets will respond and whether the matter could create a 
new obstacle to a start treaty 
