said we dont think it will work 
with 14 million men indias military is the fourth largest in 
the world after the soviet union china and united states the air 
force has 870 planes and is third behind moscow and washington in 
heavy combat airlift capacity 
india has built a blue water navy including two aircraft 
carriers with britishmade harrier jets 
in 1988 a sovietmade nuclear submarine joined indias 16 
conventional subs 
since independence from britain in 1947 indias soldiers not 
its diplomats have played the key role in most foreign policy 
crises 
a border dispute with pakistan over kashmir led to war in 1948 
and again in 1965 in 1971 indian military intervention in the 
pakistani civil war helped create the new nation of bangladesh from 
east pakistan 
india annexed goa a portuguese colony on its western coast in 
1961 by sending in the army 
the next year a border dispute with china brought india its 
only major defeat china seized 38000 square kilometers 15000 
square miles during the short war middleaged indians still talk 
about the humiliation 
most recently indian troops spent 32 months trying to quell a 
guerrilla uprising in sri lanka the island nation off its southern 
coast the last troops withdrew march 24 
in november 1988 indian paratroopers thwarted an attempted coup 
in the maldives during a recent trade dispute with landlocked 
nepal india closed 13 of the 15 border crossings and curtailed the 
passage of essential goods 
